OL,3,CDonald Trump tells BBC to apologise by
OL,4,CFriday or face billion-dollar lawsuit
OL,6,FDonald Trump has given the BBC a
OL,7,Fdeadline of Friday to retract "false"
OL,8,Fand "defamatory" statements made about
OL,9,Fhim in a Panorama documentary, or face
OL,10,Fa billion-dollar lawsuit.
OL,12,FThe US president threatened legal
OL,13,Faction after a report from Michael
OL,14,FPrescott, a former external adviser to
OL,15,Fthe BBC's editorial standards
OL,16,Fcommittee, raised concerns that a
OL,17,Fspeech Mr Trump had made before the
OL,18,Fattack on the US Capitol on January 6
OL,19,F2021 had been selectively edited by
OL,20,Fthe BBC.
