OL,3,CDonald Trump tells BBC to apologise by
OL,4,CFriday or face billion-dollar lawsuit
OL,6,FThe letter, from Trump counsel
OL,7,FAlejandro Brito, demands that "false,
OL,8,Fdefamatory, disparaging, and
OL,9,Finflammatory statements" made about Mr
OL,10,FTrump must be retracted immediately.
OL,12,FCritics said the Panorama edit was
OL,13,Fmisleading and removed a section where
OL,14,FMr Trump said he wanted supporters to
OL,15,Fdemonstrate peacefully.
OL,17,FA BBC spokesperson said: "We will
OL,18,Freview the letter and respond directly
OL,19,Fin due course."
