OL,3,CDonald Trump tells BBC to apologise by
OL,4,CFriday or face billion-dollar lawsuit
OL,6,FThe letter says if the BBC "does not
OL,7,Fcomply" Mr Trump will be "left with no
OL,8,Falternative but to enforce his legal
OL,9,Fand equitable rights, all of which are
OL,10,Fexpressly reserved and are not waived,
OL,11,Fincluding by filing legal action for
OL,12,Fno less than 1,000,000,000 dollars in
OL,13,Fdamages."
OL,15,FThe White House may also consider
OL,16,Frestricting the corporation's access
OL,17,Fto "open press events" as a result of
OL,18,Fthe edit, according to a senior
OL,19,Fofficial quoted in the Telegraph.
