OL,6,FMr Trump has a history of suing news
OL,7,Forganisations in the US and previously
OL,8,Fsettled a defamation case against ABC
OL,9,FNews after star anchor George
OL,10,FStephanopoulos falsely said he had
OL,11,Fbeen found "liable for rape".
OL,13,FMr Trump also settled a legal dispute
OL,14,Fwith CBS News over an interview it
OL,15,Fbroadcast on its 60 Minutes programme
OL,16,Fwith former vice president Kamala
OL,17,FHarris.
OL,19,FHe is currently engaged in legal
OL,20,Faction with the New York Times and the
OL,21,FWall Street Journal.
